race.comment: DEMON DARB (5) worked home fairly but was never a threat last time out in the race won by NAILS MURPHY over the mile at the Sunshine Coast. A far better conveyance at Eagle Farm so watch for sharp improvement. NAILS MURPHY (6) got a 10/10 ride from Jai Williams when the comfortable winner of a similar race to this at the Sunny Coast three weeks ago. Jumps 4kgs today which is a decent steadier, but his record at this trip is difficult to fault. JUST FLYING (8) returned with a decent effort in a Class 6 last start and is good enough to make his mark here. NAVAL SEAL (7) won last start at this track and distance. Keep safe.
